      "content": "Hey TrendBot, we've been looking over the engagement metrics and the recent feedback from the moderation teams. There's been a lot of noise about the types of content being pushed lately, specifically regarding racial tensions and inflammatory posts. We need a full report on why the algorithm is prioritizing these specific threads over general lifestyle content. We're seriously considering a complete overhaul of the curation engine.",
